column2: SELECT  s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.z as z,g.oii_#_flux, g.oii_#_eqw, g.oii_#_flux, g.oii_#_eqw,g.neiii_#_flux, g.neiii_#_eqw,p.dered_g as g_color,p.dered_z as z_color,p.dered_r as r_color,w.w1mpro as w1,w.w2mpro as w2,w.w3mpro as w3 FROM WISE_xmatch AS x JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON x.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecPhotoAll  WHERE  SpecPhotoAll.nChild = # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_g > # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_z > # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_r > #) AS p ON x.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecObjAll  WHERE  SpecObjAll.z < # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_g > # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_r > #) AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid JOIN (SELECT * FROM GalSpecLine  WHERE GalSpecLine.oii_#_flux > # AND GalSpecLine.oii_#_flux > # AND GalSpecLine.neiii_#_flux > # AND GalSpecLine.oii_#_eqw < # AND GalSpecLine.neiii_#_eqw < # AND GalSpecLine.oii_#_flux > #*GalSpecLine.oii_#_flux_err AND GalSpecLine.oii_#_flux > #*GalSpecLine.oii_#_flux_err AND GalSpecLine.neiii_#_flux > #*GalSpecLine.neiii_#_flux_err) AS g ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE (s.class = &&& or s.class = &&&)
